originalText.text: Today Wednesday 11/17- I don’t know who trained this guy but I’ve never seen bus drivers do this!!!! 1 WHY ARE YOU STOPPING AT EVERY STOP??!! Are you kidding me! No one hit stop and 15 times already he pulls over and no one is even standing there. But the kicker is, I was digging for my mask to get on, he abrasiively says , “ No one cares about masks anymore.” To which I replied excuse me? To no response. Honestly all the people in the back were not understanding what the problem was. Sometimes you get the guy that says hello in like 20k languages, cute first 5 rides. Continuity between drivers and following the same rules would be greatly helpful for riders
